WEBVTT

00:00.240 --> 00:02.400
Yaay!

00:02.400 --> 00:06.120
Tomorrow I’ll have my first date with Takeshi-san since I came back from America.

00:06.300 --> 00:07.300
I’m so excited.

00:07.610 --> 00:08.570
I wonder what to wear.

00:09.630 --> 00:15.130
I better not wear anything too flashy, or there will be more rumors about me.

00:17.610 --> 00:22.470
I haven’t bought many clothes lately.

00:23.300 --> 00:26.280
It's hard to go buy clothes at this time of day.

00:28.790 --> 00:31.320
I can’t go buy clothes during my date.

00:32.080 --> 00:34.260
I can’t do that in front of Takeshi-san.

00:34.680 --> 00:37.140
I don’t want him to get a bad impression about me.
